description:
My HoneyDew this week is the man of many voices, Josh Robert Thompson! Josh grew up in a rough Cleveland neighborhood in the early '80s. He never had the chance to meet his real father before his dad died. We talk about growing up without a dad, Josh’s depression after The Late Late Show ended & humiliating himself in front of his entire school.
